OL,3,CFootballer Christian Eriksen collapses
OL,4,Con pitch during Denmark game
OL,6,FFootballer Christian Eriksen is
OL,7,Fconscious and "doing well" after
OL,8,Fcollapsing during a friendly match
OL,9,Fbetween Denmark and Ukraine.
OL,11,FThe former Tottenham and Man United
OL,12,Fplayer was seen putting his hand to
OL,13,Fhis chest in the 65th minute of the
OL,14,Finternational friendly at Nature
OL,15,FEnergy Park in Odense, Denmark, before
OL,16,Fhe fell to the ground.
OL,18,FThe Danish Football Association later
OL,19,Fsaid Erikson was conscious and
OL,20,F"feeling well under the circumstances"
OL,21,Fas the game was abandoned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
