OL,3,CFootballer Christian Eriksen collapses
OL,4,Con pitch during Denmark game
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FEriksen previously suffered a cardiac
OL,12,Farrest and had to be resuscitated on
OL,13,Fthe pitch during Denmark's opening
OL,14,FEuropean Championship group game
OL,15,Fagainst Finland in 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
