PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780942271
OL,3,CFootballer Christian Eriksen collapses
OL,4,Con pitch during Denmark game
OL,6,F"He will now undergo further
OL,7,Fexamination at the hospital to
OL,8,Fdetermine what caused the incident. We
OL,9,Fare in constant contact with him and
OL,10,Fthe doctors at the hospital.
OL,12,F"But Christian is doing well, and he
OL,13,Fasked me to say hello to all the
OL,14,Fplayers and let them know he's okay."
OL,16,FEriksen's pacemaker allowed him to
OL,17,Freturn to his football career after
OL,18,Fhis 2021 collapse, which shocked fans
OL,19,Faround the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
