PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780942271
OL,3,CFootballer Christian Eriksen collapses
OL,4,Con pitch during Denmark game
OL,6,FAt the time several medics had to work
OL,7,Fquickly to give Eriksen chest
OL,8,Fcompressions, while his teammates
OL,9,Fformed a circle around him to shield
OL,10,Fthe scene from public view.
OL,12,FHe gained consciousness and was later
OL,13,Ftaken to a Copenhagen hospital.
OL,15,FNeither Denmark nor Ukraine have
OL,16,Fqualified for the 2026 World Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
